description: Crumbs Bake Shop, Inc. sells various cupcakes, cakes, cookies, and other baked goods. The company provides its products through its online portal. Crumbs Bake Shop, Inc. was formerly known as Crumbs Holdings LLC and changed its name to Crumbs Bake Shop, Inc. in October 2011. The company was founded in 2003 and is headquartered in New York, New York.
